text: The 2010 Florida Commissioner of Agriculture election took place on November 2, 2010, to elect the Florida Commissioner of Agriculture. The election was won by Adam Putnam who took office on January 4, 2011. ==Republican== ==Democratic== ==References== https://web.archive.org/web/20110727130144/http://enight.dos.state.fl.us/Index.asp?ElectionDate=11%2F2%2F2010&DATAMODE;= Category:Florida Commissioners of Agriculture Category:Government of Florida
title: 2010 Florida Commissioner of Agriculture election
